headline: Lisa Detanna, Global Wealth Solutions Group of Raymond James, Named to Barron’s Top 100 Women Financial Advisors
summary: BEVERLY HILLS, Calif., August 01, 2025--Congratulations to Lisa Detanna, Managing Director, of the Global Wealth Solutions Group of Raymond James located at 9595 Wilshire Blvd, Suite 801, Beverly Hills, CA 90212, on being recognized #8 on Barron’s 2025 Top 100 Women Financial Advisor lists, release July 2025.
